        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/251/302",
        "text": [
          "٢٥١. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَرَارَةُ الدُّنْيَا حَلاَوَةُ الْآخِرَةِ، وَحَلاَوَةُ الدُّنْيَا مَرَارَةُ الْآخِرَةِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "251. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: The sourness of this world is the sweetness of the next world while the sweetness of this world is the sourness of the next one."
          ]
        }
      }
